    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Utter a Name</i> is a challenging detective adventure with strong emphasis on atmosphere and investigation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213430/extras/6dcb99387a3efb5b01be559a0b2c8f5c.poster.avif?t=1743599000\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213430/extras/6dcb99387a3efb5b01be559a0b2c8f5c.webm?t=1743599000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213430/extras/6dcb99387a3efb5b01be559a0b2c8f5c.mp4?t=1743599000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several disembodied souls linger in the premises of this old manor...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must explore the vicinity and gather information.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What happened here? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who were these people? And... who killed them?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Memory 'windows' into the past that reveal important clues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A desolate estate</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several identity puzzles to solve</p></li></ul>",
